description:
The predictions for our future are dire.

The world is burning, not just by the wildfires.

Our planet is also burning with rage, war, pollution, inflexibility and insensitivity of human beings.

We have successfully paved our way to the moon and soon enough we will land on Mars, yet we are mindlessly destroying our home planet in every possible way.

Is there still a chance to reverse the damage we have done? We don't know, maybe we are already too late or maybe we still stand a chance to turn it around. We will only know when we try. 
However, we need to do it fast, our only option is to do it right Here right Now.

And even then, perhaps, doing our best is still no longer good enough..

